sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Employee Browser
    participant N as Nuxt SSR Server
    participant G as Go API
    participant C as In-Memory Cache
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    B->>N: GET /dashboard
    N->>G: GET /api/v1/config (org_id from session)
    G->>C: lookup org_id
    alt cache hit
        C->>G: config JSON
    else cache miss
        G->>DB: SELECT branding_configs + system_settings
        DB->>G: config rows
        G->>C: store (TTL 5m)
    end
    G->>N: 200 config JSON
    N->>B: HTML (config hydrated in __NUXT_DATA__)
    Note over B: Zero extra config request — config is in the HTML

    B->>G: (user actions, NOT config re-fetching)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over B,DB: Admin saves branding change
        B->>G: PATCH /api/v1/admin/config/branding
        G->>DB: UPDATE branding_configs
        DB->>G: success
        G->>C: delete org_id entry
        G->>B: 200 updated config
        B->>B: useRuntimeConfig().refresh() → update local state
    end
